!! About this plugin

This plugin allows you to do a search in the sidebar while having the results displayed in a sidebar tab -- without hiding other sidebar tabs!

@@color: #BF7C00; ⚠ Please note:@@ We want this mechanism to be implemented directly into TiddlyWiki. So if you like this plugin, please support us by writing a positive comment at GitHub [[TiddlyWiki issue 1066|https://github.com/Jermolene/TiddlyWiki5/issues/1066]] or the corresponding [[google group|https://groups.google.com/forum/#!topic/tiddlywiki/bTiOu_migHs]].

